videoSnippet.title: Actress, Model and World Chess Champion
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Lola Lefevre:

When you were 23 years old, you already demolished three shots.
- beauty doesn't rhyme with empty brain
- intellect does not rhyme with round glasses and white buttons
- women are perfectly fit to use their brains in chess
All adds up to a good dose of audacity
Alexandra Kosteniuk World Champion between 2008. and 2010.

Alexandra Kosteniuk vs Carol-Peter Gouw
Corus (2000), NED, rd 5, Jan-25 
French Defense: Two Knights Variation (C00)

1. e4 e6 2. Nf3 d5 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e5 Ne7 5. h4 c5 6. Nb5 O-O 7. c3 Ba5 8. d4 a6 9. Nd6 cd4 10. Bd3 dc3 11. Bh7 Kh8 12. Kf1 cb2 13. Bb2 f6 14. Ng5 fg5 15. Qh5 Ng8 16. Bg8 Kg8 17. hg5 Rf2 18. Kf2
